================================================================================
SCOPE
================================================================================

This license covers everything in this repository (`e1m-spec`):

  - STANDARD.md                — prose specification.
  - pinout/v1.json             — canonical machine-readable pinout (E1M).
  - pinout/x-v1.json           — canonical machine-readable pinout (E1M-X).
  - pinout/schema/             — Loom format JSON Schema.
  - examples/                  — reference SoM manifest snippets.
  - source/altium-*.tsv        — authoritative pin-list exports from Altium.
  - source/_build.py           — builder that generates pinout/*.json.
  - CHANGELOG.md, README.md, LICENSE.

